---
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Subscribe — India EV Bus Digest</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Weekly email digest of India's electric bus market — tenders, OEM orders, and registration data. Free." />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      :root {
        --green: #16a34a; --green-light: #dcfce7; --green-dark: #14532d;
        --gray-50: #f9fafb; --gray-100: #f3f4f6; --gray-200: #e5e7eb;
        --gray-500: #6b7280; --gray-900: #111827;
      }
      body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--gray-50); color: var(--gray-900); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
      nav {
        background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        padding: 0 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; height: 56px;
      }
      .nav-brand { font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; color: var(--green-dark); text-decoration: none; }
      .main { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 48px 24px; }
      .card {
        background: white; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08); padding: 48px 40px;
        max-width: 480px; width: 100%; text-align: center;
      }
      .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .sub { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray-500); margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .perks { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
      .perk { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 14px; }
      .perk-icon { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

      /* Buttondown embed form */
      .bd-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
      .bd-form input[type="email"] {
        width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 15px;
        border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius: 8px;
        font-family: inherit; outline: none;
        transition: border-color .15s;
      }
      .bd-form input[type="email"]:focus { border-color: var(--green); }
      .bd-form button {
        width: 100%; padding: 13px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
        background: var(--green); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px;
        cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; transition: background .15s;
      }
      .bd-form button:hover { background: var(--green-dark); }
      .fine-print { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-500); margin-top: 12px; }

      footer { padding: 24px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-500); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav><a class="nav-brand" href="/">🚌 EV Bus Tracker</a></nav>
    <div class="main">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">⚡</div>
        <h1>India EV Bus Digest</h1>
        <p class="sub">
          Every Monday — new tenders, OEM order disclosures,
          and Vahan registration data in your inbox.
        </p>
        <div class="perks">
          <div class="perk"><span class="perk-icon">📋</span><span>Live tenders from CESL and state STUs — with bus counts and deadlines</span></div>
          <div class="perk"><span class="perk-icon">📢</span><span>BSE order disclosures filtered for e-bus signals — no noise</span></div>
          <div class="perk"><span class="perk-icon">📊</span><span>Monthly Vahan registration snapshot by maker</span></div>
          <div class="perk"><span class="perk-icon">🆓</span><span>Free. No spam. Unsubscribe any time.</span></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Replace YOUR_BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME below after you create your account -->
        <form
          action="https://buttondown.com/YOUR_BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME/api/emails/embed-subscribe/YOUR_BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME"
          method="post"
          target="popupwindow"
          onsubmit="window.open('https://buttondown.com/YOUR_BUTTONDOWN_USERNAME', 'popupwindow')"
          class="bd-form"
        >
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
          <input type="hidden" name="tag" value="ev-bus-tracker-site" />
          <button type="submit">Subscribe — it's free</button>
        </form>
        <p class="fine-print">Sent every Monday morning. Unsubscribe in one click.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer>India EV Bus Tracker · Data from public sources · Updated daily</footer>
  </body>
</html>
